				While stern corporate tax <a href="/Historical-Tax-Rates/3020.html">rates</a> with his left hand, Mr. Obama would increase tax <a href="/Tax-Rate-In-California/5160.html">rates</a> with his right by radically increasing tax rates on dividends and capital gains. Today's economic theory and empirical evidence—including a series of papers by one 
		<br><br>
